Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------AVAN-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是格林威治标准时间23:40
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 一个旧世界正走向终结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而新的世界即将诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后 首相官邸「拉普拉斯」上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将举行由地球联邦政府主办的换历典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于挣脱地球母亲的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈入在宇宙中营造新家园的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜 我们将成为历史的见证人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们与所有人共享这份幸运的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀着感谢与感慨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目送渐行渐远的西历时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而随着新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙世纪的脚步声越来越近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们用笑容迎接它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 西历
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到宇宙世纪！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住在地球与宇宙中的所有人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是地球联邦政府首相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里卡多·马瑟纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西历即将成为历史…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}…首相或总统发言的对象向来都是本国民众
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}所谓国家 是国民与领土的统治机构
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}归根结底仅仅是为保障本国安全而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}如今 我们已实现了统一政权这一人类的夙愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}有资格批判旧定义国家的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}正如人无法独自生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}孤立的国家也无法发挥其功能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}特别是针对地球危机这一课题…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}旧制度国家从未展示出任何有效解决对策
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}如今为了解决这些已没有退路的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimsun\i1\fs23}我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:44.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\fs26}（宇宙世纪）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会引发更大规模的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后行将百年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去 地球圈难逃闭塞一途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲与宇宙世纪的不正抗争的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已开始出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望值得托付「拉普拉斯之盒」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那些人中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡帝亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个世界可能会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我以外 还有谁能原谅您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:14.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(1100,1200)}机动战士高达UC 独角兽
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------MAIN-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米诺夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗浓度 加紧散布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测敌舰为克拉普级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Clop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测到热能弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁隔离壁 快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰射出高热源体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测为机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量2…不 是3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭葛兰雪的速度足以摆脱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Garencieres
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认目标 有脚程快的杰钢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(556,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Jegan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是特装式样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明这不是偶然的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离暗礁宇域还需10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾完早些回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲·库鲁兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹帝利 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Kashatriya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.61,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(600,600)}（注：里瓦科纳船货社）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想打船的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖章佬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始返航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场由吉翁公国发动的宇宙移民者独立战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一年战争」在葬送了半数人类的性命后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿·巴瓦·库战役为界划下了句点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是17年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们出生前一年的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后也屡有自称吉翁残党的集团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起过多次战乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫嚣的宇宙移民者独立 究其根本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎根在基连·扎比主张的选民主义土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍根深蒂固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁·戴肯所提倡的吉翁主义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即所谓的新人类思想 从结果上来看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是孕育反动分子的危险思想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小看历史课 以为对求职没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使想当工人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿纳海姆也不会雇佣连高中都毕不了业的呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻信那些号称百分百就业率的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班克洛夫老师 穿梭机又出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的穿梭机也该换艘新的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是理事长太抠门？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么阿纳海姆的淘汰品就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说今天得住在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没带换洗衣服来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 明天参观「蜗牛」的计划算泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 要在这里听两天班克洛夫的特别讲习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我的话 两分钟就能讲到夏亚之乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷 是扎古
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班老头 有这种东西怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西 很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是机动战士的元祖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 仔细看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争早结束了 多看无益
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半禁止拍照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说就是不懂浪漫 这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 巴纳吉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常见你看着远处若有所思的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 刚才也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该不是在看什么地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在想「究竟是在哪儿」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 说我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论做什么 都好像没有真正经历那段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种的话 我也会有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错位的感觉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还会越来越强烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种感觉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}只是少数一帆风顺的幸运儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再踩深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备冲进那片碎石带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降至 060
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}RX-0 最终测试项目完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Final Phase all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}精神感应框架 耐G负荷良好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Psyco-Frame G-force retain in expected parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}机师生命指标正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Pilot's life signs stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们返航了 盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿纳海姆工业专科学校的自修设施中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似还有人滞留
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该事先确认过课程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的往返穿梭机似乎发生了故障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被谁的肉眼捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至多不过是一瞬间的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与月神2的幕僚们取得了联系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所属于隆德·贝尔的舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Londo Bell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与「黑袖章」接触一事貌似属实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然泄露了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发生交战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付出了损失三架机动战士的代价 毫无斩获
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他动向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试探了隆迪尼昂的口风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,439)\fs22\fsp0}（Londenion：隆德·贝尔据点）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令是个老顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫布莱德·诺亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死盯补给部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自可窥得舰队动向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位放下手头的工作听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至此 RX-0的试运行实验全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在删除所有测试用OS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封存「NT-D」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动「拉普拉斯程序」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:48.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(250,400)}（巴纳吉·林克斯 科技部资源开发系）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 5号闸门停靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来让我们见识见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拉普拉斯之盒」是个什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有的话 就带走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱的话 突围而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（和接驳通道的增压连接完毕）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ECLS各系统连接确认）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（船内电源切换至码头方面完毕）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冷却循环系统连接确认）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.61,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（推进剂补给连接臂已连接）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（气密再确认）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（维持1大气压无减压状况正常）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里瓦科纳船货社0610航班系统作业完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…失重综合症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还得去参观「蜗牛」 放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你昨晚兴奋过头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地盘机组有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 很少有机会去内部看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 上厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(0,300)}（充电中）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说借就借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真空不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要日出了 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(250,0)}（燃料警报）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬紧牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 危险 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 没事吧 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座卫星上的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否送我去「卫星建造者」的入口处？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去「蜗牛」那儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还能运作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料耗尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同电池一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多了 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去见一个人 有话和他说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快的话 会发生无可挽回的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能阻止 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止…阻止什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人到不了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想见的人 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜗牛…大家都这么称呼「卫星建造者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那里其实就是座工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说毕斯特财团的宅邸坐落在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没亲眼见过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校的理事长是财团大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当局发布治安管制警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次列车将在当前站台暂时停留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,400)}待确认安全后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}最近太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆在这儿下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她乘上过这辆「特洛8」？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有声张
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被联邦的眼线察觉会节外生枝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能根据财团的动向判断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要稍加留心 原本可以发现她的偷乘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要负责的话 也是我这个船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以猜到她想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先一步安排人手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止她与卡帝亚斯·毕斯特见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低调些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是地盘机组？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 建造地盘的作业部件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座卫星才刚刚造了一半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊 肚子不饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样最能节约时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边走边吃有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工专的参观马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后见机行事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明白自己的身份…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是考虑到自己的身份才来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要做无谓的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法善用「拉普拉斯之盒」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论它究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会被弗卢·伏龙特尔横加利用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发展成为不必要的战端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该最明白才是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被赋予的力量 原本不该为这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕我们无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我还没自我介绍 我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直在喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 加油 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 巴纳吉·林克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽…奥黛丽·本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.37,0:23:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大战中王牌机师造的宠物机器人复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候特流行对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住得偏僻…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏僻？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说居无定所 更贴切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 和我一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇呜 好多轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.99,0:24:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！从没见过那种骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看看 米寇特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.01,0:24:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.93,0:24:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 坠落在我们校庭的那辆「特洛8」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.10,0:24:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是坠落 是迫降啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.15,0:24:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道他为什么那么干
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别乱说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.40,0:24:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一害他被勒令退学 就没脸见他了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.35,0:24:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他无依无靠的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.54,0:25:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追你的那伙人 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.88,0:25:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.24,0:25:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是偷跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.17,0:25:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞政治运动的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…反联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.82,0:25:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙移民者的自治独立 是不是这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.55,0:25:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.14,0:25:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也许比你想像的更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.40,0:25:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要阻止战争
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.17,0:25:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.75,0:25:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新建成的地盘不断被推出
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民卫星的外壁得到扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.84,0:25:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观 世界在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主大人 这是刚才第二升降梯的监视器拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.89,0:26:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.34,0:26:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.54,0:26:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌晨接到人工太阳服务通道被人入侵的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.03,0:26:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.44,0:26:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黑袖章」有消息吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.44,0:26:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚无
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.54,0:26:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人行为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.55,0:26:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能对「盒」的交接造成妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.85,0:26:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若让人看见身为毕斯特财团家主的您
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.61,0:26:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与「黑袖章」成员直接会面…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.76,0:26:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…少年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 貌似是其同行者
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.20,0:26:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为警卫似乎略显年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.49,0:26:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.90,0:26:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真的在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.79,0:27:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.58,0:27:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.30,0:27:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.56,0:27:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 别随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.90,0:27:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.56,0:27:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我唯一的愿望」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.05,0:27:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能读懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.52,0:27:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 我认识这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.81,0:27:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.75,0:27:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.12,0:27:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「贵妇人与独角兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.19,0:27:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据称是中世纪前在法国制造的织锦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.70,0:28:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非仿造品
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.65,0:28:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年战争以前
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.14,0:28:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上代煞费苦心才弄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.78,0:28:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人是当代家主 卡帝亚斯·毕斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.35,0:28:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为擅闯贵宅的无礼表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.85,0:28:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.70,0:28:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久仰大名
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.71,0:28:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻您不必自报家门
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.37,0:28:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么恕我失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.15,0:28:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要您能理解我的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.66,0:28:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来此是想请求您重新考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.64,0:28:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将「拉普拉斯之盒」交付我方的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.83,0:28:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.57,0:28:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了 你我这样会面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.88,0:28:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛尼曼为人谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.97,0:28:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会制造多余的混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.27,0:28:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护您是多余的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.82,0:28:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说「拉普拉斯之盒」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.13,0:28:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毕斯特财团长期繁荣稳定的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.21,0:28:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要将其交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.49,0:28:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才让你先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.11,0:29:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在被人追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丢下她一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.13,0:29:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位小姐为何 被谁追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.94,0:29:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.89,0:29:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但是那些人很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.03,0:29:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.30,0:29:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.94,0:29:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活像新人类的口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.77,0:29:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.59,0:29:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的前途将毁于一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.23,0:29:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并非让你就读阿纳海姆工专的父亲的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.05,0:29:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.45,0:29:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生的情况尽在我掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.36,0:29:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以将品行恶劣的学生开除学籍
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.75,0:29:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.11,0:29:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你带我到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.42,0:29:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我自己能应付
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.53,0:29:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽 我要帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.08,0:29:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来阻止战争的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.15,0:29:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人有那种能力 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的战争这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.05,0:29:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和学校老师口中的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.41,0:29:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有分量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.77,0:29:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感受到它的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.71,0:30:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.03,0:30:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.55,0:30:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上 我看到你从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.26,0:30:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到一阵心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.86,0:30:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的错位感顿时消失
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像第一次看见了自己该呆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.61,0:30:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要说你需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.57,0:30:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.60,0:30:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.88,0:30:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再和我扯上关系为好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.85,0:30:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英明的决断
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.12,0:30:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已变更了约见的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.20,0:30:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦时机允许 便让你们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.04,0:30:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有重新考虑的余地了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.71,0:30:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白您的忧虑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.95,0:30:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗卢·伏龙特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.12,0:30:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为夏亚再临的那个男子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.88,0:31:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也略有耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.93,0:31:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 即便能获得「钥匙」
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.73,0:31:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有相应资质的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.95,0:31:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也打不开「拉普拉斯之盒」
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.12,0:31:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「盒子」的「钥匙」？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.95,0:31:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中略有机关
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是匹烈马
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必追了 你回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.39,0:31:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团发来了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.58,0:31:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎要将交易地点从中央港口改为卫星建造者
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.33,0:31:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于殿下的事怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.27,0:31:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯装不知
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.05,0:31:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知在打什么算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.11,0:31:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只好冷静应对了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.04,0:31:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去 为防紧急事态做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.45,0:31:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.96,0:32:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主大人亲自出迎 不胜惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.58,0:32:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团的命运在此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.72,0:32:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能假手于人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.44,0:32:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜货
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.24,0:32:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆德·贝尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.89,0:32:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙哪儿冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.46,0:32:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「钥匙」…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.95,0:32:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将得到的不是盒子本身
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.55,0:32:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是只有钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.68,0:32:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.44,0:32:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说不满意 更令人不解
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.71,0:32:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至不知道盒子究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.71,0:32:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说一旦打开就能颠覆联邦的「拉普拉斯之盒」
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.24,0:32:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因有此杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.20,0:33:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕斯特财团才能有今日的荣华
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.56,0:33:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承接美术品卫星运送的所谓公益集团
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.68,0:33:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是对外而言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.49,0:33:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.38,0:33:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵方高层承认了「盒子」的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才派您这名干将来此
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.60,0:33:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对钓在眼前的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.20,0:33:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处境不允许我们再思前顾后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.82,0:33:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这里面下了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.55,0:33:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头想必会失望至极吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.05,0:33:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长您相信新人类的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.39,0:33:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处战场有时不得不承认这股力量的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.73,0:33:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.00,0:33:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有亲身体会过的人才会如此形容它
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.39,0:33:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到宇宙的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.40,0:33:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为适应这浩瀚的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.10,0:33:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令自己的所有潜在能力开花结果
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.51,0:33:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可与他人相互理解毫无隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁·戴肯曾提出的新人类论
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.41,0:33:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在于人类的革新 无限的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.37,0:34:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究其根本 讴歌的便是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.52,0:34:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰雪 有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.33,0:34:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆德·贝尔包围了卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.03,0:34:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从收获一年战争的胜利以来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.46,0:34:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说联邦始终受制于这无形的力量也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.27,0:34:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够揭发地球特权阶级恶行的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.73,0:34:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够唤醒被视为弃民的宇宙移民者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.10,0:34:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.71,0:34:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以颠覆百年联邦统治的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.31,0:34:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙是属于宇宙移民者的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.77,0:35:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与这股无形力量的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.45,0:35:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗费了联邦数十年来的大部分精力
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群被地球引力牵着跑的狗崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.12,0:35:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新吉翁万岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.47,0:35:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:35:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔博 联系得上舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.29,0:35:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.43,0:35:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米诺夫斯基粒子也在变浓
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.37,0:36:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在卫星里打？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.22,0:36:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面到处是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能从内部杀出一条血路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.85,0:36:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到船长离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.59,0:36:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.12,0:36:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 设立的所谓官方研究机关
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.07,0:36:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实质上是针对新人类的兵器特征进行人工强化的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.17,0:36:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯狂科学家的实验场
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内忧以克里普斯战役为甚
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外患有两次新吉翁战争在目
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.80,0:36:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过度镇压招致的军阀抬头
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.62,0:36:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽令联邦疲惫不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.58,0:36:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们拥有确保胜利的强大后援
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.72,0:36:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.50,0:36:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.17,0:36:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.50,0:36:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古只认成王败寇的民众们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.43,0:36:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厌倦了没有明确的定义
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.45,0:37:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只展现出一点可能性的「新人类」概念
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.60,0:37:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个称呼不知何时起 成为了击坠王的同义词
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.68,0:37:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与曾几何时吉翁·戴肯倡导的互相理解的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.67,0:37:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到了对立面
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.98,0:37:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.95,0:37:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.66,0:37:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拉普拉斯之盒」拥有改变未来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 该说是寻回本应有的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.11,0:37:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 并非任何人都能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.56,0:37:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若使用不当 它亦可化身灭世之物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.36,0:37:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就先给我们「钥匙」来个测试？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.03,0:37:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若各位是只拘泥于单个理念的狭隘的主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.73,0:37:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「盒子」是不会展现其内容的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.67,0:37:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何为单个理念？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.88,0:37:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁的再兴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.51,0:38:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隆德·贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.80,0:38:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告称战火已蔓延至卫星内部
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.13,0:38:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.75,0:38:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被设计了 可以这么理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.22,0:38:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽想质疑各位是否被人跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.55,0:38:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是无果的争论了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.61,0:38:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把她还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.72,0:38:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至终是这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.65,0:38:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人正被安置在寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.48,0:38:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人与人彼此信任实属难事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.12,0:39:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 家主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.56,0:39:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深有同感 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.76,0:39:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.58,0:39:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别缠着不放
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.36,0:39:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.87,0:39:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.68,0:40:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.57,0:40:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星开了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.36,0:40:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一带可是学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.35,0:40:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.13,0:40:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.00,0:40:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.58,0:40:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.74,0:40:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.12,0:41:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.35,0:41:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.63,0:41:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百年的盟约也如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.39,0:41:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦打算趁机收缴一切
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.64,0:41:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我们先有意破坏盟约
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.62,0:41:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔 决不能让它落入联邦之手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.18,0:42:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.61,0:42:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.34,0:42:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.05,0:42:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧 大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.48,0:42:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓也
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.03,0:43:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔 马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.20,0:43:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼斯 托姆
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.96,0:43:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.10,0:43:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米寇特
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.76,0:43:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都上哪儿去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.40,0:43:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓也 米寇特就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.20,0:43:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.38,0:43:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去救个人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.57,0:43:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这里过去的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.49,0:43:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.77,0:43:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是Z系的可变机
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.03,0:43:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是联邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.21,0:43:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 「蜗牛」那里应该有它的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.71,0:43:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寻求保护
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.12,0:43:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉 别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.23,0:43:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,470)}米寇特！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.36,0:43:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}我不要和你分开
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.95,0:43:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.37,0:43:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是特种部队
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.91,0:44:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令室恐怕也…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.94,0:44:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就直接删除程序
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.55,0:44:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把「独角兽」…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.00,0:44:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主大人 您先走
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.09,0:44:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.64,0:45:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.49,0:45:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.79,0:45:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系不上玛莉妲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.74,0:45:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莎指使你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.74,0:45:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为利用了军部
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.53,0:45:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正被利用的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.01,0:45:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯特…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.10,0:45:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.06,0:46:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉妲
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.59,0:46:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.03,0:46:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.12,0:46:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.51,0:46:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民吗 别待在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.77,0:46:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.82,0:46:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.53,0:46:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.55,0:46:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.52,0:47:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了 是联邦的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.13,0:47:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RGZ-95 是ReZel
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.66,0:47:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米寇特
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.48,0:47:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是工专的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.93,0:47:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星破了个洞 来这里避难
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.24,0:47:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求保护
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.61,0:47:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.33,0:47:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.53,0:48:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.87,0:48:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.88,0:48:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 奥黛丽在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.28,0:48:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.84,0:48:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人她曾多次大难不死
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.22,0:48:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道把她丢下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.80,0:48:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算用这架机动战士自己逃命？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.73,0:48:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算逃脱 也时日无多
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.82,0:48:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.60,0:48:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满口大道理 也没看你做成什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.34,0:48:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽为阻止战争去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.73,0:48:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是因为你有这份能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.62,0:48:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还想着明天 想着下周要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.17,0:48:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种…不该是人的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.34,0:49:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少妈妈她…我的母亲不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.09,0:49:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更庄严 至少更…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.70,0:49:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不同于动物
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.15,0:49:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不该死得一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.19,0:49:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们这些成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.39,0:49:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却导演了太多无谓的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.65,0:49:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.92,0:49:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还蚕食地球
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.33,0:49:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向宇宙索要排泄口
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.88,0:49:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在到了人类进行自律并找回尊严的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.06,0:49:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为继承百年前遗留下的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.12,0:49:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「倾其蕴藏的可能性」
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.33,0:49:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「将人类独有的力量和善良昭示给世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.84,0:49:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独人类拥有神明
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.73,0:49:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有超越现在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.75,0:49:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是内在「可能性」之神
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.42,0:49:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有自信牢记来时的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.86,0:49:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她背负的东西可不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.09,0:50:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与她同行 需要有将整个世界放在肩上的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.51,0:50:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.68,0:50:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信和觉悟什么的 谈不上
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.28,0:50:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想她需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.48,0:50:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.28,0:50:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 它只听从你一个人的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.38,0:50:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要它认为你配得上
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.54,0:50:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽就会发挥出独一无二的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.54,0:50:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(256,438)\fnarial\fs18\b0}Unicorn
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.35,0:50:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往「拉普拉斯之盒」的道路迟早也会向你敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.96,0:50:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拉普拉斯之盒」？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.26,0:50:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束缚我们毕斯特一族长达百年的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.51,0:50:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果善加利用
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.51,0:50:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以给当今宇宙世纪带来一丝光明
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.31,0:50:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.71,0:50:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.35,0:50:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为让你免遭束缚…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.57,0:51:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才从我的眼前…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.95,0:51:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜一定恨我 想必你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.27,0:51:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.96,0:51:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畏惧 相信自己身上蕴藏的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.64,0:51:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要竭力而为 道路自然会向你敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.19,0:51:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今说这些…太自私了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.96,0:51:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.45,0:51:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想与你说更多…更多
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.86,0:51:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.40,0:51:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望实现了 安娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.82,0:51:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.69,0:51:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？ 我刚才是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.57,0:51:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.55,0:52:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我唯一的愿望」
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.10,0:52:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「可能性之兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.08,0:52:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望的象征」
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.25,0:52:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.46,0:52:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.03,0:52:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.47,0:52:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.14,0:53:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥黛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.28,0:53:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.51,0:53:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.87,0:53:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.55,0:53:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里…从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.14,0:53:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.33,0:54:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落它
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.36,0:54:15.23,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(0,350)}（新人类毁灭系统）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.07,0:54:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.27,0:55:02.29,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(0,800)}第一话「独角兽之日」
